Examples to show the use of pimglib
===================================

basic
======
	This is a very basic example to show the use of pimglib. This shows
the usage of the "pimg_load" and "pimg_free" functions. It shows how the 
image can be loaded and displayed on the screen.

save
=====
	This example shows the use of "pimg_save" function to save the image 
in a file.

zoom
=====
	This example shows the use of "pimg_zoom" function to zoom the image.

capture
========
	This example shows the use of "pimg_win_img" and "pimg_win_subimg"
functions to capture the window/pixmap contents and save it into a file.

angifs
=======
	This example shows, how an animated GIF file can be displayed.
